1
00:01:13,160 --> 00:01:13,840
Are you insane?

2
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:15,000
Shut up!

3
00:01:45,480 --> 00:01:46,040
What are you looking at?
Don't want to come up?

4
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:02,480
How come you're here?

5
00:02:02,600 --> 00:02:03,960
The situation downstairs can't hold him for long.

6
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:04,680
Hurry up.

7
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:36,760
You've got guts now, huh?

8
00:02:37,080 --> 00:02:38,320
Running away from home?

9
00:02:39,040 --> 00:02:40,120
A stray dog like you,

10
00:02:40,320 --> 00:02:41,080
where can you go?

11
00:02:53,480 --> 00:02:55,960
If I hadn't bumped into Lin Mojiao's car today,

12
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:57,680
do you think you could have escaped unharmed?

13
00:03:00,440 --> 00:03:01,080
Thank you.

14
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:03,200
I will repay this favor

15
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:05,360
to you in the future.

16
00:03:09,720 --> 00:03:10,400
Don't wait until another day.

17
00:03:11,160 --> 00:03:11,920
Let's do it today.

18
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:15,200
I want to eat noodles.

19
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:17,640
Okay.

20
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:25,680
The same red mole.

21
00:04:37,080 --> 00:04:38,240
At tomorrow's bidding meeting,

22
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:39,960
Lin Mojiao will definitely make a move.

23
00:04:41,640 --> 00:04:42,960
What you need to do is stay calm.

24
00:04:43,440 --> 00:04:44,480
[and be prepared for anything.]

25
00:04:47,840 --> 00:04:48,440
What's wrong?

26
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:52,960
Nothing.

27
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:28,360
It was you who killed me.

28
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:28,960
My son.

29
00:05:29,640 --> 00:05:31,000
Killing us wasn't enough,

30
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:33,160
you even wanted to kill your brother.

31
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:34,960
Lin Mojiao,

32
00:05:35,280 --> 00:05:37,080
we three will take you away now.

33
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:39,640
It was you

34
00:05:39,840 --> 00:05:41,080
who killed me.

35
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:42,840
You all deserve to die.

36
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:45,120
You all should die!

37
00:05:45,760 --> 00:05:46,960
You all should die!

38
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:48,600
You all should die!

39
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:49,840
You all should die!

40
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:50,840
You all should die!
You all should die!

41
00:06:41,400 --> 00:06:42,520
[Dear guests,]

42
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:43,200
[ladies,]
[and gentlemen,]

43
00:06:43,960 --> 00:06:45,080
[good morning.]

44
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:47,520
[Next, please welcome the president of Lanhe Group,]

45
00:06:47,640 --> 00:06:48,840
[Ms. Lan Hewei,]

46
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:49,840
to announce the results

47
00:06:49,840 --> 00:06:51,280
of the resort project bidding.

48
00:06:51,640 --> 00:06:52,200
Please welcome.

49
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:05,320
The company that won the bid

50
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:07,200
for the Lanhe Group's resort project is...

51
00:08:28,840 --> 00:08:29,800
Vivi.

52
00:08:36,040 --> 00:08:37,160
[Why are there two President Lans?]

53
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:38,520
[Could the one on stage]
[be a fake?]

54
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:49,240
Don't you have

55
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:50,400
anything you want to explain to me?

56
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:58,080
While I was unconscious,

57
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:01,040
you disguised yourself as me,

58
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:03,680
got close to my husband,

59
00:09:04,760 --> 00:09:06,200
and then set him up,

60
00:09:07,520 --> 00:09:08,640
taking over Blue Crane

61
00:09:10,520 --> 00:09:11,760
and suppressing the Lin Group.

62
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:16,040
How do you explain

63
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:18,720
all of this?

64
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:20,280
It's not like that.

65
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:36,120
We grew up together.

66
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:39,400
I had no idea you were this capable.

67
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:42,680
You really opened my eyes.

68
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:48,880
My dear sister.

69
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:51,640
Xu Meng...

70
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:55,040
She's Xu Meng?
Really?

71
00:10:08,160 --> 00:10:09,160
Xu Meng

72
00:10:09,920 --> 00:10:10,920
is dead, isn't she?

73
00:10:18,160 --> 00:10:18,640
Vivi,

74
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:20,640
don't believe him.

75
00:10:20,920 --> 00:10:22,080
He's lying to you.

76
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:22,960
Let's go.
I'll explain everything to you.

77
00:10:30,880 --> 00:10:31,960
As the real chairman

78
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:33,240
of Lanhe Group,

79
00:10:33,520 --> 00:10:34,400
I hereby announce

80
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:35,840
that the resort project

81
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:37,120
of the Blue Crane Group

82
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:39,000
will be officially handed over to the Lin Group.

83
00:10:53,640 --> 00:10:54,280
As for you,

84
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:56,760
the harm you've caused to us

85
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:59,680
and the Lin Group,

86
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:04,920
I will make you pay for it.

87
00:11:21,720 --> 00:11:22,480
Vivi,

88
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:24,360
don't trust him.

89
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:25,880
Lin Mojiao is the one who wants to hurt you.

90
00:11:25,880 --> 00:11:27,200
I didn't betray you.

91
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:29,720
Vivi,

92
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:30,760
trust me.

93
00:11:31,920 --> 00:11:32,320
Vivi,

94
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:34,000
can you come out and see me?

95
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:38,400
Vivi,

96
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:40,000
Vivi,

97
00:11:42,320 --> 00:11:43,560
don't you want to see her?

98
00:11:44,880 --> 00:11:46,600
I heard she got hurt overseas

99
00:11:47,280 --> 00:11:48,080
and hasn't recovered yet.

100
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:50,680
Vivi, don't trust him.

101
00:11:50,720 --> 00:11:52,680
Can you come out and see me?

102
00:11:54,760 --> 00:11:55,480
Vivi.

103
00:11:57,440 --> 00:11:58,960
If I hadn't seen her get plastic surgery

104
00:11:58,960 --> 00:12:00,680
to look like me,

105
00:12:01,240 --> 00:12:02,840
I would have thought you were lying to me.

106
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:31,400
I have scars on my face.

107
00:12:32,120 --> 00:12:33,160
Please respect me.

108
00:12:49,960 --> 00:12:50,920
This is so interesting.

109
00:12:52,280 --> 00:12:53,320
Who are you?

110
00:12:54,280 --> 00:12:55,920
Why am I locked up here?

111
00:12:57,440 --> 00:12:58,680
If you want money,

112
00:12:59,280 --> 00:13:00,560
just name a price.

113
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:02,040
Send it to the Lan family.

114
00:13:06,680 --> 00:13:07,280
Weiwei,

115
00:13:08,640 --> 00:13:09,640
Don't you remember?

116
00:13:10,880 --> 00:13:12,080
I'm your husband.

117
00:13:13,880 --> 00:13:15,160
What are you talking about?

118
00:13:16,280 --> 00:13:17,880
I don't know you at all.

119
00:13:20,280 --> 00:13:21,880
You really don't remember anything?

120
00:13:27,680 --> 00:13:28,440
Senior,

121
00:13:28,880 --> 00:13:30,240
I haven't been to

122
00:13:31,120 --> 00:13:32,560
Blue Crane since I came back.

123
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:34,800
Thank you for your hard work.

124
00:13:35,400 --> 00:13:36,200
From now on,

125
00:13:36,800 --> 00:13:37,720
leave it to me.

126
00:13:38,720 --> 00:13:40,000
I want to restart

127
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:41,400
the resort project,

128
00:13:41,400 --> 00:13:42,200
and

129
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:44,880
we'll handle it all ourselves.

130
00:13:46,240 --> 00:13:48,040
Why are you slandering my sister like this?

131
00:13:49,480 --> 00:13:51,360
I won't believe a word you say.

132
00:13:52,640 --> 00:13:54,280
Xu Meng wouldn't do this.

133
00:13:57,480 --> 00:13:58,080
Fine,

134
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:00,680
then watch for yourself

135
00:14:01,160 --> 00:14:02,840
if what I'm saying is true.

136
00:14:07,440 --> 00:14:08,480
She treated me like this

137
00:14:09,200 --> 00:14:11,440
and almost cost you a big project.

138
00:14:13,600 --> 00:14:15,200
Why should I care about her?

139
00:14:23,600 --> 00:14:24,160
Fine.

140
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:25,960
We'll leave her be.

141
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:27,960
You should get some rest.
